text: File:Alvinoreyguitarboogie.jpg File:AmMusicBunk78.jpg File:Bingola1011b.jpg Lists of record labels cover record labels, brands or trademarks associated with marketing of music recordings and music videos. The lists are organized alphabetically, by genre, by company and by location. ==Alphabetical== *List of record labels: 0–9 *List of record labels: A–H *List of record labels: I–Q *List of record labels: R–Z
title: Lists of record labels
